GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
SESSION LAW 2025-41
SENATE BILL 295
AN ACT TO CLARIFY VARIOUS MOTOR VEHICLE DEALER LAWS.
The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
PREVENT UNFAIR DEALER FRANCHISE TERMINATIONS AND CLARIFY RV
